data.description: Excellent location just 5 minutes to I-90 & Rt 20 access! Move right into this spacious 4 bed 2.5 bath 2-story! The recently updated eat-in kitchen boasts gorgeous new granite countertops, center island, oversized white cabinetry and Samsung appliances included! Light and bright throughout with volume ceilings and fresh neutral paint with white trim. All this with an open concept to the oversized family room which includes a wood-burning fireplace with custom floor-to-ceiling oak mantle. The master suite offers a cathedral ceiling feature with a large walk-in closet and en-suite with dual vanity, oversized soaker tub, and tile shower surround. Fenced-in back yard with paver patio, 2nd-floor laundry, new furnace in 2018, Aprilaire, HSA Warranty provided! Vinyl windows have a lifetime transferable warranty.
